text:
Songbird Nancy Ajram to inaugurate the Alexandria International Song Festival Songbird Nancy Ajram to inaugurate the Alexandria International Song Festival 2.5 5 
Published October 4th, 2015 - 07:32 GMT via SyndiGate.info Rate Article: Nancy Ajram will kick off the children's charity concert at the Alexandria International Song Festival in Oct. () Follow > Click here to add Nancy Ajram as an alert Click here to remove the Nancy Ajram alert Disable alert for Nancy Ajram Lebanese superstar singer Nancy Ajram will inaugurate the Alexandria International Song Festival on October 15 in the Sayyed Darwish hall at the Opera. Festival organizers plan to donate dividends to a children's charity. Tickets prices range between $25-63 USD. Advertisement Â© Copyright Egypt Independent. All rights reserved. Rate Article:
